trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>List Locations</languageKeyword> operation returns a list of locations to which you can ship the disks associated with an import or export job.
trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>List Locations</languageKeyword> operation returns a list of locations to which you can ship the disks associated with an import or export job.

trans-unit.source: A location is a Microsoft data center region.

trans-unit.source: Remarks
trans-unit.target: Remarks

trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>List Locations</languageKeyword> operation returns a list of addresses that you can ship your disks to for an import or export job.
trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>List Locations</languageKeyword> operation returns a list of addresses that you can ship your disks to for an import or export job.

trans-unit.source: In many cases, the list will only contain a single address, and you will need to ship your disks to that location.
trans-unit.target: In many cases, the list will only contain a single address, and you will need to ship your disks to that location.
